### Notes
- DeepSeek cannot do the pie chart
- The currency code column may contain a colon (e.g., `cn:`), leavi in, it is for obfuscation.
- Zero-padding should be applied to numeric columns (e.g., `¤n`, `Forex`, `USD equiv`) to ensure visual alignment, typically to two decimal places.
- Rounding to two decimals applies to all final displayed numbers (intermediate calculations can retain precision).



